Class AppCompatPreferenceActivity

  • com.example.chaosruler.msa_manager.activies.settings_activity.AppCompatPreferenceActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SettingsActivity

    public class AppCompatPreferenceActivity

    A android.preference.PreferenceActivity which implements and proxies the necessary calls to be used with AppCompat.
